    "description": {
      "value": "<p>By 11th level, when you have both your astral arms and visage summoned, you can cause the body of your astral self to appear (no action required) for 1 ki. This spectral body covers your physical form like a suit of armor, connecting with the arms and visage. You determine its appearance.</p><p>While the spectral body is present, you gain the following benefits:<br /><strong><br />Astral Harmony</strong>. Your unarmed strikes using your astral arms gain any magical bonuses of the weapons you are wielding.<br /><br /><strong>Astral Deflection</strong>. The damage reduced and damage you deal with your Deflect Harm is increased by your Wisdom modifier (minimum of 1).</p>",
